{"tid":2382213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最高刑期10年，知法犯法，黑警強姦性侵6兒童獲輕判，法庭鼓吹性暴力","createTime":"2021-01-27T06:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T07:09:12.000Z","uid":292024,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"239af5077bd89e4c10fc5e88aa145fe9748488aa","tid":2382213,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:42:18.000Z","msg":"向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為<br />\n<br />\n根據 第200章《刑事罪行條例》 第146條 ，任何人向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為、或與16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為、或煽動16歲以下兒童，向任何人或與任何人作出猥褻行為，均屬違法。這項罪行並沒有指明性別，即是說，男性或女性都可以干犯這項罪行。<br />\n<br />\n這項罪行的最高刑罰，是監禁10年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姦一個平均都係坐半年都冇，香港黑警就係有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b1162e693a95a58db961f06d00b75a2bfd741c","tid":2382213,"uid":137038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"向社會發出正面訊息，鼓勵市民投考警察"},{"pid":"3c894a5f2d6a58c937beb0d527820c3837aac5f3","tid":2382213,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0945cf75da5e0116ed6ec81c6d5ecd9c1247b2c7","tid":2382213,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"抵啦 拜登一定會鐘意香港呀！"},{"pid":"7a4b2cfd2f1c7033f250a584ca4b67966a344316","tid":2382213,"uid":155682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"呢個時候一定唔見蕭芳芳喇"},{"pid":"46e1fdbddf4aa1fac34e1ae2d55615e22ce094e8","tid":2382213,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞六個細佬 咁都判咗輕 咩道理"}]}